      <div id="ya">  <h2 id="contents">Aarav Sharma(I like to call him Aarav Shawarma)</h2>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Aarav.S is not smart
            <li>Everyone knows that
            <li>He is struck by dumbness
            <li>As well as disgustingness hat
            <li>He likes to do gross stuff
            <li>Like pick his nose
            <li>Just talking about him wants to make me take a bath
            <li>Somebody, grab the hose!
            <li>He is so dumb as well
            <li>From his toes
            <li>to his head
            <li>Only his parents can tell what he knows
        </ul>
        <span id="stuff"><h2>The end!</h2></span>
        <h2 id="second-post">Aarav Agarwal( I like to call him Aarav Pagalwala[Crazy Man in hindi])</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Aarav Agarwal is dumb
            <li>And mean
            <li>He is dirty
            <li>I don't think he will ever be clean
            <li>He is stinky
            <li>You can smell him from the sky
            <li>Everyone will soon say to him
            <li>Good-bye!
            <li>He is also the dumbest person
            <li>I have ever met
            <li>Is he an animal?
            <li>Take him to the vet!
        </ul>
